{
  "stem": "10162.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 89.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At my trial.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was just a lesson for me that stuck for the rest of my life with Hungary, that you're not supposed to say this because it's not taken the way you, you, you give it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and the background for this is, of course, the anti-Semitism that permeated the Stalins-- Stalinstad communism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You probably remember, also, you know, the Jewish doctors trials.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was horrendous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We all knew that these are trumped-up charges and far-fetched.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it started in Russia, and then it came in S-- the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then it was coming toward Hungary, also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, of course, communism is really like a religion and doesn't tolerate any other religions, but least of all it tolerated Jewis-- Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were not supposed to-- just not supposed to say anything about that ever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, which also adds another dimension of what we went through-- Hungarian Jews or Czech Jews or Polish Jews who went back for one reason or the other.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if you-- those who came to the United States or to France or Switzerland or to a free Western type-- style democracy were able to pick up the pieces and make a life for themselves.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But like we went from, from one thing into the other, one, one, one terrible thing into the other.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to live a lie for so many years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, anyway, I was in this marriage, and I, I just knew that this, this is-- this cannot last.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's something.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have to find some kind of a solution.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the summer of 1956, I decided to get a divorce because the children were two and three, and I just didn't want them to grow up and to be old enough to hear this, this man who, who would come home at the wee hours of the, the night and, and, and go into a rage and break furniture.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want to jump out of the window and go to jump in the Danube.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this went on all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I got a divorce, and-- which didn't quite end it, because he kept coming back and saying, you know, saying that he will change and all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, in 1956, October, which was two months after my divorce, the Hungarian revolution broke out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I did have some part in the revolution because I used to go to these clandestine meetings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wasn't an anti-communist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was an anti-Stalinist, an ant-- anti-totalitarian form of, of communism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I certainly wasn't for, for imperialism or, or the country being run over by any, any other superpower.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I just had enough of all this, and I, I wanted justice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was going to these meetings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't do anything more heroic than that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's what-- that's what everybody did who was in my situation until, suddenly, the, the atmosphere was such that it was really enough to lit that legendary match and the whole thing would explode.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody thought that, that anything could happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then when the Hungarian revolution just erupted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the children were, by the divorce process, given to me anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I grabbed the two children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went out, and I left the country, went to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it wasn't hard because during those week or 10 days, the borders were open.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody was going in every direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was-- in, in, many ways, it was a beautiful revolution because the Hungary was united to one man.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
